<h1>Have you tried morning planning, <%= @user.name %>?</h1>

<p>Starting your day with a few minutes of intentional planning can make a huge difference. It's one of the most powerful habits you can build.</p>

<p><strong>Here's how it works:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Choose your <strong>top 3 priorities</strong> for the day</li>
  <li>Write a brief <strong>daily intention</strong> to guide your mindset</li>
  <li>Add any <strong>tasks</strong> you want to accomplish</li>
</ul>

<p>The whole process takes less than 5 minutes, but the clarity it brings lasts all day.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @app_url %>" class="button">Start Morning Planning</a>
</p>

<p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> Try doing your morning planning before checking email or social media. You'll start your day focused on what matters most to you.</p>

<p>Happy planning!</p>
